  </table> 
 </div> 
</div> 
<p><strong>Scouring Black Flame</strong> is an <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Incantations" href="/Incantations" target="">Incantation</a> in <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Wiki" href="/Elden+Ring+Wiki">Elden Ring</a>. <strong>Scouring Black Flame spell</strong> creates fire in a wide area in front of the user. Can be charged for increased range. Updated to&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Patch Notes" href="/Patch+Notes">Patch 1.07</a>.</p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<div class="lineleft"> 
 <p><em>A black flame incantation of the Godskin Apostles.<br><br>Sweeps a wide area before the caster with black flame.<br>Charging enhances range.<br><br>The black flame could once slay gods. But when Maliketh sealed Destined Death, the true power of the black flame was lost.</em></p> 
</div> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Where to find Scouring Black Flame</h3> 
<p>Where to find <strong>Scouring Black Flame</strong>:</p> 
<ul> 
 <li> <p>Dropped by <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Godskin Apostle" href="/Godskin+Apostle" target="">Godskin Apostle</a>. <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Interactive Map?id=5817&amp;lat=-78.01562&amp;lng=100.75492&amp;zoom=8&amp;code=mapA" href="/Interactive+Map?id=5817&amp;lat=-78.01562&amp;lng=100.75492&amp;zoom=8&amp;code=mapA">Elden Ring Interactive Map Link</a></p> </li> 
</ul> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Elden Ring&nbsp;Scouring Black Flame Guide</h3> 
<ul> 
 <li><a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Godskin Apostle Incantations" href="/Godskin+Apostle+Incantations" target="">Godskin Apostle Incantation</a></li> 
 <li>Stamina Cost: 36</li> 
 <li>Deals fire damage</li> 
 <li>Travels outward and upward in an arc from the player, making it tough to deal with smaller enemies on the ground like Rats or Dogs 
  <ul> 
   <li>This can be somewhat mitigated by free-aiming the camera downward before casting</li> 
  </ul> </li> 
 <li><span style="color: #ff6600;"><em>Notes:</em></span>&nbsp;As of&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Patch Notes" href="/Patch+Notes">Patch 1.07</a>, increased stamina attack power against guarding enemies and increased poise damage when charged.</li> 
</ul> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
